    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "+ql7A4RBiSSEeY7zuYwHyzdCSESHcUJGBIpDtxvR75c=",
    "originContent": "## Always watching. Always ready.",
    "translatedContent": "## 时刻监控，随时待命。"
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "nBffvDx5Na8SE/XSUgdhqJWoOsmIt5eh84+PzJ8T2Co=",
    "originContent": "Most AI tools wait to be asked. CORE watches.",
    "translatedContent": "大多数AI工具都在等待请求。而CORE在观察。"
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 76,
    "rowsha": "zLPiWMBj5k5gmY3yYbVAtx6IJTLs9w9DPe4Vd0uDVos=",
    "originContent": "Connect it to your apps and it monitors activity across all of them. An email arrives from a client, a GitHub issue gets assigned, a Sentry alert fires, a meeting ends. CORE sees it, checks your memory and the skills you have set, and either handles it or surfaces it for your judgment. You do not trigger it. It notices on its own.",
    "translatedContent": "将它连接到你的应用，它会监控所有应用的活动。客户的一封邮件到达，GitHub问题被分配，Sentry警报触发，会议结束。CORE会看到这些，检查你的记忆和已设置的技能，然后要么自动处理，要么呈现给你判断。你无需主动触发它。它会自动注意到。"
  },
  {
    "row": 77,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 78,
    "rowsha": "5y2AGPKnFm2UpvF1TzguaIrV+h+Gj6TX79dsk0jsCqM=",
    "originContent": "Install the CORE plugin in Claude Code, Codex, or Cursor and your agent conversations get watched too. Context discussed, decisions made, code written, all of it feeds the memory knowledge graph. The next task CORE picks up already knows what happened in your last session.",
    "translatedContent": "在Claude Code、Codex或Cursor中安装CORE插件，你的代理对话也会被监控。讨论的上下文、做出的决定、编写的代码，都会反馈到记忆知识图中。CORE接下来的任务已经知道你上一轮发生了什么。"
  },
  {
    "row": 79,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 80,
    "rowsha": "9w8sx/WNJHBy2CFujHJir5acmbTyOg4s4HFn6H5ctRo=",
    "originContent": "When it acts, it acts directly. It can reply to emails, update Linear issues, file GitHub PRs, send Slack messages, run terminal commands, drive a browser, and spawn a Claude Code or Codex session from any interface. Send a WhatsApp message from the airport and CORE can have a coding session running and a PR open before you board.",
    "translatedContent": "它行动时，直接行动。它能回复邮件、更新Linear问题、提交GitHub PR、发送Slack消息、运行终端命令、驱动浏览器，并可从任何界面启动Claude Code或Codex会话。从机场发送WhatsApp消息，CORE可以在你登机前就启动编码会话并打开PR。"
  },
  {
    "row": 81,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "你可以决定它自主操作的范围，以及哪些地方需要等你指令。比如，自动处理 Sentry 警报，但合并代码前总是询问你。编码会话开始前需要你批准方案。任何邮件发出前都需确认。每个任务、每个应用、每个动作的自主等级都可自定义。"
  },
  {
    "row": 82,
    "rowsha": "iD34rtiEXxWMq8IN+tt/Jn+NvpQUgwoyn7llSVAsvb8=",
    "originContent": "You decide where it acts on its own and where it waits for your call. Handle Sentry alerts automatically but always ask before merging. Approve a plan before a coding session starts. Require confirmation before any email goes out. The level of autonomy is yours to set, per task, per app, per action.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 83,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 84,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 85,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 四种交互方式"
  },
  {
    "row": 86,
    "rowsha": "qaGFxyoFGUN33X8Nw6cSFef4zNO1MfIt/irtubLDwIE=",
    "originContent": "## Four ways to reach it",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 87,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "聊天机器人只有一种界面，操作系统有很多。"
  },
  {
    "row": 88,
    "rowsha": "V7UCxWVvTbwqjcwogDpA1/g6TFaKwcm8g5jEuxtmt2A=",
    "originContent": "A chatbot has one interface. An OS has many.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 89,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "**语音。** Mac 上按 Ctrl+Option，说出你要做的事。CORE 在后台运行，不打断你的工作流。"
  },
  {
    "row": 90,
    "rowsha": "P/R8uyl7v4JjKT/8lIfX9EMAtgWaMHKl5AdMbSvoWfo=",
    "originContent": "**Voice.** Press Ctrl+Option on Mac and say what needs doing. CORE runs it in the background without breaking your flow.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 91,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "**便签。** 打开你的每日页面，写下 `[ ] 修复第 #47 号问题中的认证 bug`。CORE 会在 3 分钟内识别，自动从你的代码库和记忆中加载上下文，并草拟解决方案。"
  },
  {
    "row": 92,
    "rowsha": "VIUxpY+VAV3j0T6+ABe1kVxEpG4g1DRNEeV2Emoc4pk=",
    "originContent": "**Scratchpad.** Open your daily page and write `[ ] Fix the auth bug from issue #47`. CORE picks it up within 3 minutes, loads context from your repo and memory, and drafts a plan.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 93,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "**消息。** WhatsApp、Slack、Telegram。无论是在机场、手机上还是床上，都能发送任务。CORE 能获取你的全部上下文，不论消息来自哪里。"
  },
  {
    "row": 94,
    "rowsha": "ne3pNqzB5diNDqkei46ILgpfSu9fFiK8nZyuEJseQHU=",
    "originContent": "**Messaging.** WhatsApp, Slack, Telegram. Send a task from the airport, from your phone, from bed. CORE has your full context regardless of where the message comes from.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 95,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "**对话。** 打开仪表盘，直接与之对话，就像与任何助手交流一样。当你想在委托前多聊几句时。"
  },
  {
    "row": 96,
    "rowsha": "bBM3kEHMtq6FjZzl7fjh3H5gpel0i58iHBp9yaBHxBU=",
    "originContent": "**Chat.** Open the dashboard and talk directly, like any assistant. When you want a back-and-forth before delegating.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 97,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "一个 AI，四种界面，背后始终共享同一记忆和上下文。"
  },
  {
    "row": 98,
    "rowsha": "LEyali0YF0/IubE8fsZI0l6RdVZrbZzPsjXehGZLvVY=",
    "originContent": "One AI, four surfaces, the same memory and context behind all of them.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 99,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 100,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 101,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 个性化定制"
  },
  {
    "row": 102,
    "rowsha": "m47gJRxyuhNRnwoWjLM8Abl1ew+BwVqb4VkEc/6gXMo=",
    "originContent": "## Make it yours",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 103,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "给它起个名字。选择它的说话风格。设置它在各处遵循的规则。"
  },
  {
    "row": 104,
    "rowsha": "b2PvehKG7dEnsfqP28Vx0bEQDHiM6ewXKGsL5ZNmcwU=",
    "originContent": "Give it a name. Choose how it speaks. Set the rules it follows everywhere.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 105,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "可选五种内置人格——TARS 的冷静高效、Alfred 的忠诚正式、Hudson 的温暖务实——或自定义你的专属人格。无论是执行任务、草拟方案，还是代你发送消息，个性都会贯穿始终。"
  },
  {
    "row": 106,
    "rowsha": "PuqirftWj0juNMaL1zs3hjqc9j4yMx7n2JfHiWFHC8E=",
    "originContent": "Pick from five built-in personalities — TARS's dry efficiency, Alfred's loyal formality, Hudson's warm practicality — or write your own. The personality carries into every task it runs, every plan it drafts, every message it sends on your behalf.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 107,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "选择语音交互时的声音。从此以后，无论在哪个界面，它都会以你配置的方式发声和行动。"
  },
  {
    "row": 108,
    "rowsha": "UQj7OsCYqCG21uhVCjUdhCLdxc4MNygLbU10YPh5ea0=",
    "originContent": "Choose its voice for spoken interactions. From then on, it sounds and behaves like the AI you configured, across every interface.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 109,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 110,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 111,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## CORE 实际应用"
  },
  {
    "row": 112,
    "rowsha": "rgP15XtCRgj5lFXu+JL6bERkStGaMgAZqO04IUVDf+k=",
    "originContent": "## CORE in action",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 113,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### 说出需求，回来就是一个 PR。"
  },
  {
    "row": 114,
    "rowsha": "5BqjS+UkcdrNnJbAVdqmfozymvWDoVk9xEIBP9gJb/8=",
    "originContent": "### Say it, come back to a PR.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 115,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "*按 Ctrl+Option，说：* “修复第 #312 号问题中结账流程的竞态条件。”"
  },
  {
    "row": 116,
    "rowsha": "mjj/dEu2+kZMYo5VzOHxg77k8bEHYwiI7Th3l5nqFCw=",
    "originContent": "*Press Ctrl+Option, speak:* \"Fix the race condition in the checkout flow from issue #312.\"",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 117,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "CORE 加载问题，提取相关提交和 Slack 讨论，拟定方案，并启动 Claude Code 会话。你回来时，已经有了 diff。全程无需坐在工位前。"
  },
  {
    "row": 118,
    "rowsha": "6AM4sOHU+r9U+5D6fHy2YieKnwl9v3eSnup2pLKFIQU=",
    "originContent": "CORE loads the issue, pulls related commits and Slack threads, drafts a plan, and runs a Claude Code session. You come back to a diff. You were never at your desk.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 119,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### 晚上写下任务，早上来审查。"
  },
  {
    "row": 120,
    "rowsha": "ohIWyhFq0V01Vo4sguUc2jY/rOwfCuphnUtFO4LEMTg=",
    "originContent": "### Write it at night, review it in the morning.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 121,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 122,
    "rowsha": "CoyFpSIJN/6OEHxY6zd/jndlpsEXJ4jxMd4F9dH6a8Q=",
    "originContent": "*Scratchpad:* `[ ] Work through tonight's backlog starting at 11pm`",
    "translatedContent": "*便签:* `[ ] 从今晚11点开始处理未完成的工作`"
  },
  {
    "row": 123,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 124,
    "rowsha": "jXH+LSzBdT1trNKGX6/PIUy1FFRdjkjrAMVxCzfX5LI=",
    "originContent": "CORE pulls from Linear, GitHub, and memory, prioritizes, and works through it while you sleep. Smooth runs are waiting for your review. Stuck sessions come back with one tight question, not a stalled tab.",
    "translatedContent": "CORE从Linear、GitHub和记忆中拉取内容，进行优先排序，并在你睡觉时完成处理。顺利的流程等待你审查。卡住的流程只带回来一个精准的问题，而不是停滞的标签页。"
  },
  {
    "row": 125,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 126,
    "rowsha": "SSorHz96JCOEdTDkT362t7qgVhoJazAaWZZHNcB7hVI=",
    "originContent": "### Message it from anywhere.",
    "translatedContent": "### 随时随地发送消息给它。"
  },
  {
    "row": 127,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "bsmUG+b5aW4KvLXX47MM9BWrQWLDbyd4W3pq2Rx9XcM=",
    "originContent": "*WhatsApp from the airport:* \"Ship the auth refactor.\"",
    "translatedContent": "*在机场用WhatsApp:* “发布认证重构。”"
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "3CJCJCHBsYgvlgwsy0T+iijoYPrqO0oNjXhej8sjw+4=",
    "originContent": "CORE already knows the branch, the context, and your preferences. It is running in Railway. It kicks off the session before you board.",
    "translatedContent": "CORE已经知道分支、上下文和你的偏好。它在Railway上运行，在你登机前启动流程。"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "jRddimP8S5Cl/HHChvyS/zn9BMXtBXRPr15FPajotaM=",
    "originContent": "### Investigate alerts before they become incidents.",
    "translatedContent": "### 在警报变成事故前调查问题。"
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "ZWjuIa53FlkJ542zJWWnH+fKuMZS18DDAJ4oKpuV68g=",
    "originContent": "*Sentry fires at 2am.* CORE investigates, pulls related traces and prior incidents from memory, proposes a fix, and pings you on Slack: \"Issue #847, fix proposed, awaiting your review.\" You approve from your phone.",
    "translatedContent": "*Sentry在凌晨2点触发。* CORE调查，拉取相关追踪和历史事件，提出修复方案，并在Slack上通知你：“Issue #847，已提议修复，等待你审查。”你用手机批准。"
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 136,
    "rowsha": "WWuWp/79+HjVuAIt7+8g49e0+UAj0mNYrygqBJtaDEg=",
    "originContent": "### Get a brief that already knows your week.",
    "translatedContent": "### 获取已知你本周情况的简报。"
  },
  {
    "row": 137,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 138,
    "rowsha": "Av6XfsyCJMNWTe735wqA+80DG+TA1syoW5T6Qvd7i4Y=",
    "originContent": "*Recurring task, every morning at 8am.* CORE pulls from email, GitHub, Linear, and Slack, surfaces what actually needs attention, skips what does not, and turns follow-ups into tasks automatically.",
    "translatedContent": "*每天早晨8点的周期性任务。* CORE从邮件、GitHub、Linear和Slack拉取内容，优先显示真正需要关注的事项，跳过无需处理的内容，并自动将后续事项转为任务。"
  },
  {
    "row": 139,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 140,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 141,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 142,
    "rowsha": "gYvdrRUMSB/TAZ2ICoUdHi4JJfWnfcnMPCCtOnhOU2A=",
